10 must-follow dogs of Instagram 
Daily Dot Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Instagram ?already boasts over 2 million followers--and with good reason. The photo-sharing platform is a perfect social 
destination for dog-lovers.?For your doggy delight and delectation, we've gathered together our 10 favorite Fidos that can be found being adorable over on Instagram.?...
